2026-06-29T03:09:27+00:00	openclaw.audit	{"payload":{"type":"TOOL_POLICY_EVALUATION","spiffeId":"spiffe://example.org/ns/apps/sa/gateway-1","agentId":"1e87bb7c-30ef-4ee0-9510-87694b6294af","toolName":"write","params":{"path":"testing.md","content":"# Testing\n\nA blank page waits, a quiet hum,\nThe cursor blinks for what's to come.\nWe poke, we prod, we run the test,\nTo separate the worst from best.\n\nEach edge case lurks, a hidden snare,\nThe bug that wasn't really there—\nUntil you ship, and then it grins,\nAnd that's precisely where it begins.\n\nSo write it down, then watch it break,\nRepeat for clarity's own sake.\nFor code untested, smooth and proud,\nIs just a guess that's said out loud.\n"},"timestamp":1782702566932},"signature":"MEYCIQDyuEAbePc2JsD4+XJ2fR+jtNemf5fBb1Xu5EWqNf4dDAIhAMjEi8dcUDRyQHGxhWrpoeV4xJdi3vRdCBd9YtJ3+eEb"}
